# V1 Dogfooding Log — Scope

First real use session: 2026-04-28

---

## Bugs found and fixed

### Sidebar stale after project mutations
After creating or deleting a project on /projects, the sidebar project list didn't update until a manual page reload. Root cause: Next.js layout cache wasn't invalidated.
**Fix:** call `revalidatePath("/", "layout")` from the project create, rename, and delete API routes.

### Delete project fails silently when it has issues
The production DB was missing migration 0001 (`ON DELETE set null` on the issues FK). Deleting a project with issues threw a FK constraint error that the API swallowed and the UI ignored.
**Fix:** wrap DELETE in try/catch, return 409 on failure, show an alert in the UI. Applied migration 0001 directly via Supabase SQL editor.

### New issue dialog: project pre-fill shows stale value on first open
When navigating between project filters client-side, `NewIssueButton` stays mounted so `useState(defaultProjectId)` doesn't re-run. First open showed the previous project.
**Fix:** `useEffect` on `defaultProjectId` to keep state in sync with the prop.

