## Improvements made

### Demo / read-only mode
CV reviewers need access without the admin password. Added `DEMO_SECRET` env var: logging in with it gives a read-only session. All mutation API routes return 403 for demo sessions. UI hides create/edit/delete controls and shows a "demo" badge in the sidebar.

### Dark mode button contrast
Chrome's "Enable automatic dark mode" was double-converting the already-correct colors. Added `color-scheme: light` / `color-scheme: dark` to CSS and `<meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">` to the root layout so Chrome knows the page handles dark mode natively.

### Pre-fill project when creating issue from a filter view
When /issues is filtered by a project, opening the new issue dialog now pre-selects that project.

### Create a project inline from the new issue dialog
Added a "+ New" link next to the project dropdown. Clicking it swaps in an inline input — type a name, confirm, and the project is created and auto-selected without leaving the dialog.

### Issue title character limit (200 chars)
Added a hard cap of 200 characters on issue titles, with a counter that appears in the last 40 chars and turns red in the last 10. Applies to both the create dialog and the issue detail editor.
